column8: Mostly sunny. The chance of fog early this morning. Light winds becoming southeast to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h in the afternoon then becoming light in the late evening.

Cloudy. The chance of morning fog in the northeast suburbs. Medium (50%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Light winds.
